<h2>2016</h2>

<div class="callout--icon-left icon-forward">
<h3><strong>Daylight saving starts </strong><time datetime="2016-10-02T02:00">Sunday 2 October 2016 at 2:00am</time></h3>
<p>Put your clocks forward by 1 hour</p>
</div>

<p>Daylight saving is observed in the Australian Capital Territory, New South Wales, South Australia, Tasmania and Victoria.</p>

<p>Daylight saving is not observed in the Northern Territory, Queensland or Western Australia.</p>


<h2>2017</h2>

<div class="callout--icon-left icon-back">
<h3><strong>Daylight saving ends </strong><time datetime="2017-04-02T02:00">Sunday 2 April 2017 at 2:00am</time></h3>
<p>Put your clocks back by 1 hour</p>
</div>

<div class="callout--icon-left icon-forward">
<h3><strong>Daylight saving starts </strong><time datetime="2017-10-01T02:00">Sunday 1 October 2017 at 2:00am</time></h3>
<p>Put your clocks forward by 1 hour</p>
</div>

